{"word":"πέτασος","slug":"πέτασος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n82734\" key=\"pe/tasos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πέτᾰσ-ος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, also <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eratosth.\">Eratosth.</a></author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:499e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.499e</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πετάσῳ Θετταλικῇ</foreign> is prob. cj. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πίλῳ Θετταλικῇ</foreign> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:4:8:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HP\">HP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.8.7</biblScope> </bibl> (cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9</biblScope> </bibl>) : (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">πετάννυμι</etym>) :—<sense id=\"n82734.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">broad-brimmed felt hat</tr_>, worn by <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔφηβοι</foreign> and hence used as their badge, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:10:164\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.164</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γυμνάσιον καθίδ